metadata.name: Dusky Love
metadata.description: Why go with society's generic definition of love? Why there just be a white Taj Mahal? Our love is unique to us just like our life experiences. Then why go with white? Why can't mine be pink under the blood-red moon in the sky of my imagination? My pink Mahal is as much as valid as somebody's blue or green. Our stories are unique and each one deserves to be expressed and loved.
